Regulation (EEC) No 4252/88 is hereby amended as follows:
1. in Article 4(2), "1 April 1999" and "1 September 1999" shall be replaced respectively by "1 April 2000" and "1 September 2000";
2. in Article 6(2), "1 April 1999" and "1 September 1999" shall be replaced respectively by "1 April 2000" and "1 September 2000".
